These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, project-manager, librarian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, siglo
1. the videographer is the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Job   | videographer | librarian | project-manager    |
| Cigar     | old-henry    | siglo       | bongani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
House: townhouse, colonial, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, february
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
4. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| House     | cape-cod | townhouse | colonial  |
| Birthday   | august  | october  | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, tram, ship
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Transport           | ship | tram | boat |
| Sport   | surfing        | ice-hockey    | lacrosse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cricketing, bluemaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, skateboarding
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the cricketing-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the cricketing-smoker##3
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | cricketing | siglo |
| Sport     | rugby  | cricket    | skateboarding  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, biathlon
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Sport   | skiing | tennis | biathlon |
| Pet     | fish   | cat   | guinea-pig   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, horse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Pet   | horse | dog | mouse      |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero  | adventure | comedy |

