2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday   | december  | september    | november       |
| Pet   | hedgehog | turtle | guinea-pig |

