.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, aconite
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, librarian, pilot
1. the person who growsorchid is the police-officer##1
2. the librarian is in the middle##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the police-officer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Flower   | aconite        | poppy  | orchid   |
| Job       | pilot | librarian | police-officer |

