.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
3 different games are played: poker, chess, domino
City: hannover, hamburg, miami
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Game           | poker | chess | domino |
| City   | miami    | hannover | hamburg     |

