2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
