.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
House: gothic-revival, palace, futuristic
City: london, boston, new-york
1. the person traveling to london is between the gothic-revival house and the palace house##2
2. the person traveling to boston is the palace house##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| House      | palace    | futuristic    | gothic-revival  |
| City   | boston | london | new-york |

