.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, kale, watermelon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsmarigold##2
4. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Food   | mango | watermelon | kale |
| Flower           | daisy    | balloon-flower    | marigold       |

