2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the designer##3
3. the designer is the designer##1
4. the journalist is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | romance   | zombie |
| Job   | analyst | designer | journalist |

