.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, indonesian, pakistani
There 3 different types of food: papaya, watermelon, asparagus
1. the person eating watermelon is in the middle##1
2. the pakistani is between the person eating asparagus and the person eating papaya##2
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the indian##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | pakistani | indian |
| Food   | papaya     | watermelon  | asparagus    |

