.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, collecting, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, march
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby          | collecting | woodworking    | camping |
| Birthday   | march      | october | august  |

