.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding, skiing
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, architect, bartender
1. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the architect##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | skiing    | skateboarding | sailing         |
| Job   | bartender | architect  | security-guard |

 